Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay

description: Recently refreshed Front & center Flagship Wharf  duplex penthouse facing Boston harbor!  2/3 bedrooms, (a cozy library with a fireplace can be used as 3rd bedroom), 3 baths. Sleep in1st floor bedroom or the upper bedroom suite with adjacent sitting area, ensuite bath with double sinks, jetted tub, jet spray shower, and 2 walk-in closets . Private outdoor deck overlooks the city and harbor. Peninsula granite/stainless kitchen opens to formal dining area & living room. Hardwood floors, great closets & elegant marble formal entry.  Full service 24/7 concierge, elevator building with fitness center & sauna. 1 self park & 1 valet garage parking included. Easy access to downtown via water shuttle, water taxi, Logan airport & major highways. Located in the historic Charlestown Navy Yard surrounded by green parks, marinas & minutes to all the city has to offer!  Watch the Tall Ships sail by your private deck facing down harbor. +2100 living space. Listed $400K below city assessed value.
